data.description: Southern living at its finest in the coveted neighborhood, The Verandas, where charm & elegance meet modern convenience. This custom 2022 Parade of Homes, a masterpiece by Eric Craig Homes, is now available to make your dreams come true. With 3,369 square feet of meticulously designed living space, this gold fortified gem offers the perfect blend of sophistication & comfort. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, a dedicated office, & a spacious bonus room, this abode is ready to accommodate your every need. As you step inside, the grand foyer welcomes you with a striking brick accent wall and exposed cypress beams, setting the stage for the unique character of this residence. The living room, a true entertainer's dream, features cypress exposed beams & a cypress mantle framing a cozy fireplace. For the culinary enthusiast, the chef's kitchen is a vision of delight. Equipped with GE Cafe' appliances, Dolomite countertops, custom cabinets, & an abundant butler's pantry, this space is where culinary magic happens. The dining area, just steps away, is perfect for gathering with loved ones. This home also offers a separate, spacious office & a large laundry room for added convenience. The primary suite is the epitome of luxury, offering a spacious retreat for relaxation. The primary bath continues the opulence, with custom cabinets, tile floors, a separate shower, & a soaking tub, creating a spa-like sanctuary right in your home. Venture upstairs via the grand staircase with its wrought iron railing to discover three additional bedrooms & a generous bonus room that could easily double as an extra bedroom. An oversized landing area awaits, perfect for a kid's den & reading nook. The Verandas neighborhood itself is a treasure, located just 7 minutes from downtown Fairhope. Here, you'll enjoy a lifestyle unlike any other, with a zero-entry pool, community garden, tree-lined sidewalks & streets, & serene stocked ponds. It's not just a neighborhood, it's a lifestyle! Welcome home!
